entries.next: You've been a great help. I may have further need of you later, so don't be a stranger.
entries.cantwork: If you wish to assist me, you must first finish any other tasks you have.
entries.npc_reset_1: I'm sorry if this was too much for you. You can work for me when you're a bit more seasoned.
entries.notyet: Sorry, I'm sort of busy at the moment and don't really have anything to say.
entries.npc_1_1: A good day to you. Are you enjoying our fair city? If you're looking to make a few credits, I believe I can oblige you. Leb Slesher is an official who really knows how to enjoy himself. I want to help him have a good time; in fact, I know a lady he'd really like. I was hoping you'd escort her into town so I can arrange an introduction. Will you do it?
entries.npc_2_1: Great. Her name's Shandara. She's really terrific. Bring her here and I'll see to the rest.
entries.npc_3_1: Not interested, hmm? You're either wealthy or you keep your expenses low.
entries.npc_4_1: Well, Slesher must be important -- after all, so many important people come to see him. With all his carousing, he must have trouble getting any work done. My friend might help him keep track of his work. Anyway, are you interested in this escort job?
entries.npc_backtowork_1: So, are you going to go get Shandara?
entries.npc_reward_1: Excellent. Now I just need to arrange a chance meeting.
entries.npc_work_1: Where is Shandara? Haven't you picked her up yet?
entries.npc_noloc_1: Unfortunately, just now you're a little early to meet Shandara. Perhaps you could come back in a while, and we can arrange the meeting then.
entries.npc_failure_1: You didn't bring Shandara? It seemed like such a simple task.
entries.otherescort_1: It's just not your lucky day, is it? I'm actually waiting for somebody else.
entries.dontknowyou_1: Sorry, friend. I don't have time to chat.
entries.npc_takeme_1: You're here to bring me to Kadaara, I hope. Watch yourself -- the animals around here have been skittish lately.
entries.npc_dropoff_1: I'm glad I had you along to bring me in safely. Otherwise that trip would have been bloody. Thanks very much.
entries.player_reset_1: I don't want this mission right now.
entries.player_sorry_1: I'll keep working on the mission.
entries.player_3_1: Why do you care if this Slesher has a good time?
